# Can be used with VSC Rest Client Extensions

### get customers
GET http://localhost:8080/customer

### get user
GET http://localhost:8080/user?email=user@mail.com

### get revenues
GET http://localhost:8080/revenue

### get invoices (only 5)
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice/latest/5

### get all invoices
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice/latest/0

### get all invoices with filter for page 1
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice/filtered?query=Michael&currentPage=1

### get all invoices with empty filter 
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice/filtered?query=&currentPage=1

### create a new invoice
POST http://localhost:8080/invoice 
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "customer_id": "d6e15727-9fe1-4961-8c5b-ea44a9bd81aa",
    "amount": 100,
    "date": "2024-08-12",
    "status": "pending"
}

### set ID to id from last create request!
@ID=1726842829794
#### get invoice by id
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice?id={{ID}}

### update invoice
PUT http://localhost:8080/invoice/{{ID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": "{{ID}}",
    "customer_id": "4711",
    "amount": 200,
    "date": "2024-08-12",
    "status": "paid"
}

#### get invoice by id to check update
GET http://localhost:8080/invoice?id={{ID}}

### delete invoice
DELETE http://localhost:8080/invoice/{{ID}}

### get user
GET http://localhost:8080/user?email=user@mail.com